cu.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid value 'invalid_id' will cause identification conflicts, preventing the gNB from being properly recognized in the network and leading to registration failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting gNB_ID to an invalid value 'invalid_id' will cause identification conflicts, preventing the gNB from being properly recognized in the network and leading to registration failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB_ID 設定為無效值 'invalid_id' 會導致識別衝突，阻止 gNB 在網路中被正確識別，並導致註冊失敗。
